      <title>铁矿石价格波动，焦点为中国房地产和矿业产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/iron-ore-swings-with-china-property-and-miners-output-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国释放出进一步解决房地产危机的信号，以及两家领先的矿业公司报告季度产量增加并计划进一步扩张，铁矿石价格在涨跌之间徘徊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/iron-ore-swings-with-china-property-and-miners-output-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 02:20:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
